stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DRAFT : created from IPC / VendorInvoice / Payroll
    DRAFT --> CHECKED : voucher checker
    CHECKED --> AUDITED : internal audit
    AUDITED --> APPROVED : AG / authoriser
